Html:
From the jquery api:

.ajaxError( handler(event, jqXHR, ajaxSettings, thrownError) )


From the definition file : 

ajaxError(handler: (evt: any, xhr: any, opts: any) => any): JQuery;


should probably changed to :

ajaxError(handler: (e: JQueryEventObject, request: JQueryXHR, settings: JQueryAjaxSettings, thrownError:string )=>void):JQuery;
